freenet.support
Class TransferThread

java.lang.Object
  freenet.support.TransferThread
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientBaseCallback, ClientGetCallback, ClientPutCallback, PrioRunnable, Runnable
public abstract class TransferThread
extends Object
implements PrioRunnable, ClientGetCallback, ClientPutCallback

A thread which periodically wakes up and iterates to start fetches and/or inserts. When calling start(), the thread will iterate the first time after getStartupDelay() milliseconds. After each iteration, it will sleep for getSleepTime() milliseconds.

Author:
xor
